      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>vegetable samosa pie</strong> with the<strong> green beans</strong>, a dollop of the <strong>coriander chutney</strong> and <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
